title: Kahen Litran Diesel
info:
lyrics translated

2-liter diesel (4x)
and a basic pushchair with its frames
an engine with a new chassis model
six times one meter forty
moves slightly
yes, a bit
2-liter diesel (4x)
and a freezer, the model of year 85

a basic pushchair and Fiat or a baby carrier 
and a freezer or Fiat and a baby carrier 
or a freezer and a basic pushchair
or Fiat or a freezer and Fiat

or 2-liter diesel (4x)
2-liter, 2-liter
until breathless

(NOTE: "kahen" is dialectal, "kahden" is the genetive of "two" in standard language)
